revision.text:
[http://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plantilla:Cita_publicación Plantilla:Cita_publicación] is not an infobox - it contains information about a publication, not about the subject of a Wikipedia article - so it should not be extracted by the DBpedia mapping framework. Maybe later we can use templates like it, but not for now.

